Title: Supertech insolvency: Homebuyers in despair
Festivals: ['One World Romania - International Human Rights Documentary Film Festival', 'Vienna Shorts - International Short Film Festival', 'Zlín Film Festival - International Film Festival for Children and Youth', 'Mountainfilm Documentary Festival - Telluride', 'Festival Internacional de Cine de Alicante', 'Molodist International Film Festival', 'Krakow Film Festival']
Narrative:
Last month, the National Company Law Tribunal (NCLT) declared the real estate firm Supertech insolvent. The decision came after the Union Bank of India filed a petition against Supertech for non-payment of dues.

Over 25,000 affected homebuyers in Noida feel the latest developments could add to their woes and make their long-drawn struggle to get ownership of their flats more complicated. Is it the end of the road for homebuyers in Noida or is there light at the end of the tunnel?
